OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FHundreds of British Gas workers are
OL,7,Ffacing redundancy as the company
OL,8,Fpushes ahead with a major overhaul of
OL,9,Fits customer service operations, with
OL,10,Fthe GMB union claiming staff are being
OL,11,Freplaced by artificial intelligence.
OL,13,FBritish Gas has announced plans to cut
OL,14,F500 jobs across its Services and
OL,15,FEnergy call centre teams in Glasgow,
OL,16,FEdinburgh, Cardiff, Leicester,
OL,17,FStockport and Leeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FThe company told staff at an online
OL,7,Fmeeting on Thursday that the
OL,8,Fredundancies were part of its
OL,9,F"Customer Service Transformation"
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,FAccording to information shared with
OL,13,Fstaff, customer contacts handled by
OL,14,Fthe Energy and Services teams have
OL,15,Ffallen from around 20 million in 2023
OL,16,Fto 16 million in 2025 and are forecast
OL,17,Fto fall further to 14 million in 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
