OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBritish Gas's Energy team handles
OL,12,Fcustomer enquiries about gas and
OL,13,Felectricity accounts, including bills,
OL,14,Fcomplaints and payment difficulties.
OL,16,FThe Services team deals with
OL,17,Fbreakdowns and repairs covered by
OL,18,FBritish Gas HomeCare policies,
OL,19,Fincluding boilers, radiators,
OL,20,Felectrical appliances, drains and EV
OL,21,Fchargers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FStaff were told the changes were
OL,7,Fneeded to meet the "evolving needs of
OL,8,Fcustomers" and that British Gas would
OL,9,Fcontinue investing in digital tools.
OL,11,FThe company said around nine in 10
OL,12,Fcustomer interactions now take place
OL,13,Fthrough its website, chatbot, app or
OL,14,FWhatsApp channels, with many customers
OL,15,Fpreferring to resolve issues
OL,16,Fthemselves rather than speak to a call
OL,17,Fcentre adviser.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FThe GMB union has criticised the move,
OL,7,Fdisputing suggestions that demand for
OL,8,Fcall centre services has fallen. The
OL,9,Funion says its members report being
OL,10,Funder pressure and struggling to cope
OL,11,Fwith workloads.
OL,13,FCharlotte Brumpton-Childs, GMB
OL,14,FNational Secretary, said: "It's an
OL,15,Fabsolute disgrace British Gas is
OL,16,Fslashing hundreds of human jobs and
OL,17,Fgiving them to chatbots.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,F"These staff are massively overworked
OL,7,Fand underpaid, yet do their level best
OL,8,Fto keep customers happy. Now, instead
OL,9,Fof being rewarded, they're being
OL,10,Freplaced by artificial intelligence."
OL,12,FDocuments seen by ITV News show the
OL,13,Fcompany's Customer Service
OL,14,FTransformation strategy aims to reduce
OL,15,Favoidable contact with call centres,
OL,16,Fencourage greater use of self-service
OL,17,Fand digital channels, and reserve
OL,18,Fcontact centre support for customers
OL,19,Fwho "fall out of the digital journey."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FArtificial intelligence is
OL,7,Fincreasingly being used by companies
OL,8,Fto handle customer service enquiries
OL,9,Fthrough websites, apps, chatbots and
OL,10,Fmessaging services such as WhatsApp.
OL,12,FModern AI systems are capable of
OL,13,Fdealing with tasks such as explaining
OL,14,Fbills, taking meter readings,
OL,15,Farranging appointments, processing
OL,16,Fpayments and troubleshooting problems,
OL,17,Foften without human intervention.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,FIt is not clear to what extent British
OL,7,FGas is currently using artificial
OL,8,Fintelligence in its customer service
OL,9,Foperations.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,12,Fcompany said: "The suggestion these
OL,13,Froles are being replaced by AI or new
OL,14,Fchatbot technology is simply wrong.
OL,16,F"Customer behaviour is changing, with
OL,17,Finbound contact down by around 31%
OL,18,Fsince 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,F"While demand for call centre support
OL,7,Fhas reduced, we recognise that many
OL,8,Fcustomers still need to speak to us -
OL,9,Fparticularly those requiring
OL,10,Fadditional help - and this will always
OL,11,Fremain a priority.
OL,13,F"We have been transforming our
OL,14,Fbusiness for a number of years to
OL,15,Fensure we have the right roles in
OL,16,Fplace for the future. As part of this,
OL,17,Fand in response to the way customers
OL,18,Fare choosing to engage with us, we are
OL,19,Fconsulting on changes across our
OL,20,Fcustomer operations team that could
OL,21,Faffect around 500 roles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781330678
OL,3,CUnion says workers 'being replaced by
OL,4,CAI' as British Gas cuts 500 jobs
OL,6,F"We are working constructively with
OL,7,Four trade unions to support colleagues
OL,8,Fthrough this and we're offering the
OL,9,Foption of voluntary redundancy where
OL,10,Fpossible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
